            This app is a work in-progress, done on my own free time.<br /><br />
            Here is a list of functionalities already completed:
        </p>

        <p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Explore face groups and persons</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Detect and identify faces via web cam</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Add/update/remove groups</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Add/update/remove people</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Upload/remove person faces from URL/file upload</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Detect and identify faces via URL/file upload</li>
            </ul>
        </p>

